data.description: Ranch style home situated on 1/2 acre lot in prime Machesney Park location! Lots of potential here! Spacious living room features large bay window and coat closet near the front door with a half wall open to the eat-in kitchen. The main floor is complete with three bedrooms and full bath. The bathroom features new flooring, shower surround, toilet and vanity. There's original hardwood flooring under the carpet in the living room and bedrooms! The full basement features a large multi-functional rec room space with built-in cabinets, and large storage/utility area. Outside you'll find a fully fenced-in yard, garden shed storage, and patio area. Enjoy the 1 car ATTACHED garage--a rare find! Roof is approx. 4 years old. Property being sold "as is", no FHA or VA financing.
